Basics informations

Need a powerful pc?

It is not necessary to have an extremely powerful PC to play GTA Vice City on your computer. Although the game was originally released in 2002, it can run on a wide variety of hardware configurations, including older or less powerful computers.

minimum specifications

Processor: Intel Pentium III or AMD Athlon at 800 MHz

RAM memory: 128 MB

Video Card: 32 MB with

DirectX 9.0 compatibility

Minimum Disk space: 591 MB

Operating system: Windows 98/2000/ME/XP

disable antivirus?

It is not necessary to disable windows defender, for various security reasons it is not necessary to disable antivirus

the safety of our users will always be a priority!
